node.text:
☀️🌊🍉🌺 
Another redraw of an old piece !! 👀👀 i kinda really changed it from the old one lmao ! Swipe to the last slide to have a look ! 
Also I decided this would make a super fun #drawthisinyourstyle !!! I feel like it’s got a lot of fun elements that could be fun and challenging! Feel free to draw her in any way you like and interpret the piece in any medium ! ✨ here are the few rules !
RULES : 
- use the tag #lanajaybeach 
- post my image after your own 
- tag me @lanajay_art 
- have fun !!! 
I may not be able to feature everyone but I’ll feature as many entries as I can on my stories and choose a few favs to be shared on my page ! Have fun and I hope you guys like this piece ✨🌊

node.text:
Thought it would be fun to tackle a little redraw !!! ✨ she’s giving me major 80s space babe vibes in the new version 💫 
I found a bunch of my older art from 2014 the other day and omg my style has really changed ! I think when I drew this I’d only been drawing digitally for a year ? And definitely didn’t have an iPad or barely any understanding of digital art programs lol 
It’s always super interesting to look back and revisit old concepts ! I also ended up experimenting a little bit with a more painted look and ah I’m so happy with the result !! ✨ what do you guys think???
